<span style="font-size:1.2em;">Software Tools for Dynamic Web Sites</span></div>
<p>Founded in September 1995, HREF Tools
Corporation provides middleware that greatly reduces the time and
complexity of creating interactive, database-intensive, web-based
applications that run on Windows NT servers.</p>

<p>WebHub is a software product for people who
want fast, full-featured web sites that are easy to maintain.
WebHub provides a complete development environment for building web
applications. Its components simplify the development process with
integrated solutions to the challenges of multiuser state management,
persistent database connectivity and high level HTML page generation.
For full customization, you need to use Borland's Delphi 2 or 3.
WebHub includes runners for ISAPI, cgi-bin and cgi-win so your
application will run with any Windows NT web server.</p>

